com.dhemery.expressions.polling

Interface PollTimerPoller

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Poller

    public interface PollTimerPoller
extends Poller
    A poller that uses a PollTimer to pause between evaluations and to determine whether the schedule has expired.

        Polls the matcher's acceptance of the value that the function derives from the subject.
